 />"},{"pid":"3bc2c1260313ca9da3dbbdf36cc4ac25a7aebc28","tid":1984734,"uid":58296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc4f2f2e8a76e20d9a2997cf4ae9bb62e3a86f7","tid":1984734,"uid":66866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"醫生開左隻藥俾我都係屙軟屎 但係都會痛"},{"pid":"2184be0b271190b231db8687c826f5074d1cbc06","tid":1984734,"uid":354382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"有排我都係咁<br />\n<br />\n之後減少屙屎次數 + 狂食香蕉 + 屙屎個陣慢慢咇啲屎出嚟<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就開咗好返"},{"pid":"70f758ad3a41acbd9535fe79d15d3f15d9a406d2","tid":1984734,"uid":354382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有排我都係咁<br />\n<br />\n之後減少屙屎次數 + 狂食香蕉 + 屙屎個陣慢慢咇啲屎出嚟<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就開始好返</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3f2d3eba7ecfb823704d51336cac827dc6553a91","tid":1984734,"uid":305544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"曾經試過都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係去藥房買嗰種搽嘅藥膏，搽完已經feel到冇咁痛，過多幾日已經好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住之後基本日日飲益力多幫自己排便"},{"pid":"d300fc47b3809ce912d0950d949af25f5494ea8d","tid":1984734,"uid":204635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"之前都試過，同你一樣淨係行路都痛。<br />\n之後偷咗屋企人d 痣瘡藥黎用（塞入屎眼果d) 用幾日就好左好多。如果無既我覺得可以用vaseline 代替，訓前同痾屎前搽，得d屎唔好介爛屎眼。另外我覺得坐熱水都有用。"},{"pid":"e0f76c7b16515ac93a50207aee30bd072b393f48","tid":1984734,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"好似有舊好鋒利嘅屎喺出口附近又痾唔出﹐不停畀蕭屎𠝹到流血"},{"pid":"a441039c959071d00a5a34282de6832f5c8754fc","tid":1984734,"uid":58296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f76c7b16515ac93a50207aee30bd072b393f48","tid":1984734,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited